otin 	ext{coNP}$. We present a flaw in Lin's construction of $D$ (a nondeterministic Turing machine that supposedly recognizes $L_d$ in polynomial time). We also provide a proof that $L_d 
ot\in 	ext{NP}$. In doing so, we demonstrate that Lin's claim that $	ext{NP} 
